Package: cyclinginfra
Title: Urban Cycling Infrastructure Accessibility Analysis
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Andrea Belen", "Cretu Toma", , "acretuto@uni-muenster.de", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A tool for downloading, classifying and visualising urban cycling
    infrastructure using OpenStreetMap data. Provides S3 classes in order to represent
    cycling networks and their safety classification, together with functions for
    classifying road types by safety level and producing safety maps.
